{"arkId":"cl010114201","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010114201","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Bureau plat dit \u0022de Vergennes\u0022","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Bureau plat dit \u0022de Vergennes\u0022"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1745","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 604 - De Louis XIV \u00e0 Louis XVI - Charles Cressent","room":"Salle 604, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1745,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Dubois, Jacques","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Atelier de","dates":[{"date":"1694","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1763","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Eb\u00e9niste","authenticationType":"marque (estampilles, poin\u00e7ons...)","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3158780"},{"label":"Migeon, Pierre","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Participation","dates":[{"date":"1758","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Eb\u00e9niste","authenticationType":"marque (estampilles, poin\u00e7ons...)","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3386287"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6600","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"mobilier ; bureau plat","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Bureau plat \u00e0 quatre faces et \u00e0 trois tiroirs, plaqu\u00e9 d\u0027un frisage de bois de violette dessinant des rectangles, des losanges et des quadrilobes. Le d\u00e9cor de bronze comprend des coquilles aux angles du plateau, aux chutes des pieds et au milieu des grands c\u00f4t\u00e9s de la ceinture, des feuilles d\u0027acanthe flanquant le d\u00e9crochement du tiroir central, des tiges fleuries formant les poign\u00e9es et occupant les renoncements lat\u00e9raux. Les pieds cambr\u00e9s, reposant sur des sabots rocailles, sont rev\u00eatus de montants qu\u0027entoure une forte tige feuillag\u00e9e, en bronze dor\u00e9. Dans la ceinture sont m\u00e9nag\u00e9s trois tiroirs dont celui du milieu, en retrait, pr\u00e9sente une grande entr\u00e9e de serrure en bronze. Sur les faces lat\u00e9rales est fix\u00e9 un arbuste encadr\u00e9 de rocailles. Dessus de maroquin brun ; quart-de-rond chantourn\u00e9 et moulur\u00e9 de bronze dor\u00e9.","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"83","displayDimension":"83 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"197,5","displayDimension":"197,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"101","displayDimension":"101 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : ch\u00eane (b\u00e2ti et tiroir)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : sapin (b\u00e2ti)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : bois de violette (plaquage)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : bronze (dor\u00e9)\r\nTechnique : techniques bambou\/ bois\/ corne\/ ivoire\/ \u00e9caille (\u00e9b\u00e9nisterie)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : maroquin","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Provenant du Minist\u00e8re des Affaires \u00e9trang\u00e8res\r\nDepuis Vergennes, le bureau n\u0027aurait pas quitt\u00e9 le Minist\u00e8re des Affaires Etrang\u00e8res. \r\r\nMonsieur Raymond Poincar\u00e9, Pr\u00e9sident du Conseil des Ministres et Ministre des Affaires Etrang\u00e8res voulut bien remettre ce meuble \u00e0 la Direction des Mus\u00e9es nationaux lors de son arriv\u00e9e au Quai d\u0027Orsay, et d\u00e8s lors le meuble fut affect\u00e9 au Mus\u00e9e du Louvre. Attribu\u00e9 au Louvre par d\u00e9cret du 11 d\u00e9cembre 1912.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Minist\u00e8re des Affaires Etrang\u00e8res","note":"","role":", Institution \/ Mus\u00e9e"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"versement","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1912","startYear":1912,"endYear":1912}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"versement"}],"place":[{"value":"Paris"}],"objectType":[{"value":"mobilier"},{"value":"bureau plat"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Rosenberg, Pierre (dir.), Des m\u00e9c\u00e8nes par milliers\u00a0: un si\u00e8cle de dons par les Amis du Louvre, cat. exp. (Paris, Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, 21 avril-21 juillet 1997), Paris, RMN, 1997","bibliographyDate":"1997","bibliographyDetail":"p. 38-41","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Silverman, Debora L., L\u2019Art nouveau en France : politique, psychologie et style fin de si\u00e8cle, Paris, Flammarion,, 1994","bibliographyDate":"1994","bibliographyDetail":"p. 351","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Alcouffe, Daniel ; Dion, Anne ; Lef\u00e9bure, Amaury, Le mobilier du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, 1, Dijon, Faton, 1993","bibliographyDate":"1993","bibliographyDetail":"n\u00b0 45","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Dreyfus, Carle, Catalogue sommaire du mobilier et des objets d\u0027art du XVII\u00e8me et du XVIII\u00e8me si\u00e8cle, [Mus\u00e9e du Louvre], Paris, 1922","bibliographyDate":"1922","bibliographyDetail":"p. 23, n\u00b0 36","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000114201\/0000245068_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louv